oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: NRBQ at Ace of Clubs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: NRBQ (Musical group); Rogers, Roy, 1911-1998; Delta Rhythm Kings; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (blue on red) announcing NRBQ with Roy Rogers and the Delta Rhythm Kings at Ace of Clubs in Nashville, Tennessee on April 23. Poster features woodcuts of the suits of card (hearts, spade, diamond, and club).
